          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, re-boil half a kettle</p><p>Dissolve 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>Knorr chicken stock cube</strong> and the <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
